verbose_text: Interestingly, while TWEAK induced the expression of MAFbx in cultured myotubes [XREF_BIBR], there was no significant difference in mRNA levels of MAFbx in skeletal muscle of wild-type and TWEAK-Tg mice indicating that TWEAK might be causing muscle wasting in vivo specifically by augmenting the expression of MuRF1 [XREF_BIBR].
